This repository contains Tableau dashboards created to practise and demonstrate data‑analysis and data‑visualisation skills.  
Each project focuses on transforming raw datasets into clear, interactive insights.

## Contents
- Global Health Insight dashboard
- Data exploration and KPI visualisation exercises
- Practice dashboards for skill development

## Skills Demonstrated
- Data cleaning and preparation
- Building interactive dashboards
- Analytical storytelling
- Visual design and UX principles
- KPI creation and trend analysis
